<h4 id="toc2"><span>14 April, 1992 CE</span></h4>
<p><em>Temple of Many Hands Society</em></p>
</div>
<p>“Where have you taken us?” Cynthia asked.</p>
<p>“Well, this was somewhere I retreated to a long time ago,” Marquez said. “Its outside of the baseline reality, a pocket dimension. We shouldn’t have to worry about the Foundation or US Federal Authorities here.”</p>
<p>He turned to the twenty-odd members of the Second Haptic Assembly who had <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5512">followed him from Boston</a>.</p>
<p><em>It’ll be different this time.</em></p>
